message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for sale at $11,500.  I believe it will be very valuable for you.
Hi Alice, I appreciate the offer but $11,500 is a bit too high for me.  I'm willing to pay $10,500.  Let me know what you think.
Hi Bob, I understand your position, but $10,500 is a bit too low for me.  How about we meet in the middle at $11,000?
